overview: Dear friends, this is my 9 year anniversary DVD.  It contains material that I have written and performed with since I started as a comedian in 1993 - both new 9 year anniversary.  I have chosen not to have any "bonus material" with, for the simple reason that virtually EVERYTHING that I have made that have not previously been published, found on this DVD.
title: Anders Matthesen: 9 Års Jubilæum
